      "date": "2012-11-14 15:25:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\n> I don't see the posix test being run\n\nNot sure what's wrong with autotest.\n\nHere is the manual test result on SLES 11 SP2 clients against master branch, the baseline was ext3:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7d69f330-2d93-11e2-89bf-52540035b04c\n\nAnd this is the manual test result on RHEL6 clients, the baseline was ext4:\n\nhttps://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5d85df66-2e6f-11e2-8849-52540035b04c",
